<% if @resource.is_a?(Artist) %>
Welcome to Pickleball, <%= @resource.username || 'Artist' %>!
<% else %>
Welcome to Pickleball, Venue Owner!
<% end %>

<% if @resource.is_a?(Artist) %>
Thanks for signing up as an artist on Pickleball. We're excited to have you join our community of musicians and performers!
<% else %>
Thanks for signing up as a venue owner on Pickleball. We're excited to help you connect with talented artists and grow your venue's presence!
<% end %>

To complete your registration and access your dashboard, please confirm your email address by clicking the link below:

<%= @confirmation_url %>

IMPORTANT: This confirmation link will expire in 3 days.

If you didn't create this account, you can safely ignore this email.

---
Pickleball
<%= Time.current.year %>
